data.description: The home you've been waiting for in the Woodgate subdivision is here.  This 4-bedroom 2.5 bath home sits on the largest lot in the subdivision. There's literally nothing to do but move in. The owners have maintained and made extensive upgrades to the home to include new concrete patio 2023, new roof 2019, 12x14 Gazebo with aluminum roof 2023, hot water heater 2023, bathroom remodeled 2023, Furnace 2017, new appliances 2021, plus more. Full list of upgrades and warranties conveyed with the property are available upon request. Don't let this this home pass you by. The main level offers a spacious living room and separate dining room for all your family dinners. Generous size family room with fireplace and bar for those cozy evenings with family and/or entertaining friends. Upper level offers 4 oversized bedrooms. Huge master bedroom with full bath. This one won't last schedule your viewing today.
